import React, { Component } from 'react' // import moment from 'moment' import { Card, CardActions, CardContent, Typography, Table, TableBody, TableRow, TableCell, ExpansionPanel, ExpansionPanelDetails, ExpansionPanelSummary } from '@material-ui/core' import { withStyles } from '@material-ui/core/styles' import ExpandMoreIcon from '@material-ui/icons/ExpandMore'; import DeleteAlert from '../Alerts/DeleteAlert'; import EditQuestion from './EditQuestion'; const styles = theme => ({ card: { display: 'flex', maxWidth: '60%', margin: 'auto', marginBottom: '12px', background: '#011', [theme.breakpoints.down('sm')]: { maxWidth: '85%', }, [theme.breakpoints.down('xs')]: { maxWidth: '95%', } }, heading: { fontSize: theme.typography.pxToRem(15), fontWeight: theme.typography.fontWeightRegular, }, }); class QuestionSummary extends Component { render() { const { question, classes } = this.props; // console.log(question) return ( } style={{ display: 'flex',justifyContent:'space-between' }}>
question : {question.question}
Type : {question.questionType} Level : {question.questionLevel} Category : {question.questionCategory} Answer : {question.answer} Author : Mostafa Hazareh Issue by : {/* {moment(question.createdAt.toDate()).calendar()} */} 12.07.2019
) } } export default withStyles(styles)(QuestionSummary)
